{"tid":765433,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[中醫藥推廣--第二回　玉石部]","createTime":"2018-08-02T17:53:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-11T03:44:38.000Z","uid":185884,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e5f1bf5fb83175a231fc851fab5e9d3c14d47ed5","tid":765433,"uid":185884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T17:53:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">慈石</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n味辛寒。主治周痹風濕，支節中痛，不可持物，洗洗酸痛，除大熱煩滿及耳聾。一名玄石。生山谷。<br />\n<br />\n治子宮不收，痛不可忍：慈石酒浸，煆、研末，米糊丸梧子大。每臥時滑石湯下四十丸，次早用磁石散，米湯服二錢。散用磁石(酒浸)半兩，鐵粉（鐵落）二錢半，當歸五錢，為末。<br />\n<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/03/015302_704b27084030f0e97ce3ce3e5953e9e5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F03%2F015302_704b27084030f0e97ce3ce3e5953e9e5.jpg&h=65e2795c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7cd0612eebc0a94d213d6470cf980cab00b31767","tid":765433,"uid":185884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T12:44:25.000Z","msg":"有請連登杏林聖手馬百良平安油分享"},{"pid":"6fe7483cf3b7d17cc254fc81e748600d72573571","tid":765433,"uid":185884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T01:37:25.000Z","msg":"見有人講<br />\n不耻自推"},{"pid":"38314c1f2c89971b5c967a3129f5032cee706067","tid":765433,"uid":185884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T03:44:38.000Z","msg":"真心誠意推動中醫發展"}]}